name: eggplant
project_description: Code a website that measures the length and width of the browser window. Display the dimensions using cm or inches in a cool way - and remember to make it responsive! Extra challenge: Can you find a clever way to utilize the max/min-width property in CSS instead of using JavaScript?

name: slot machine
